STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Connell LAMB, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0059 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Connell Lamb appeals his sentences for child endangerment and domestic abuse causing bodily injury. SENTENCES VACATED AND REMANDED FOR RESENTENCING.

SENTENCES VACATED. REMANDED FOR RESENTENCING.
